    ### Party ###

    Join us at the [Erreichbar] on Friday night, 4 November for the **globale party**!

    You'll be able to enjoy a live act from Berlin-based balkan band [Tralalka] plus many DJs (including our very own [Pod]),
    and of course meet our team and guests!

    There will be **no entrance fee**!

    Erreichbar is located in the basement of the rear building, on *Reichenbergerstr. 63A (U-Bhf G&ouml;rlitzer Park)*.

    ### globale11 ###
    ![poster]{: #poster }

    *globale 2011* will take place from **3rd to 9th of November 2011** in Berlin.

    The main venue is [Kino Moviemento][moviemento], with workshops planned in [allmende e.V.][allmende] and [c-base].

    Have a look at the [program], and for further information please download the festival's [booklet]{: target="_blank" }.

    The ticket prices go from 4 to 10 Euros, with 4 as the minimum price. The rest is donation to the festival.

    We also offer a festival pass, available for 35 to 100 Euros, with 35 being the minimum. The rest is again donation to the festival.

